      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like everything is just... gone. it’s like the part of me that actually lived, the part that saw color and felt anything, just evaporated. i look at my canvases and they’re just empty white voids, and i realize i’m just a hollow shell now. there's nothing left inside me to justify why i'm even still taking up space.",
