    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just it... how can there be hope for \"rebuilding\" something that isn't there? you keep saying i'm more than my art, but the art was the only thing that made the \"me\" part real. without it, i'm just a biological machine going through the motions. it feels like a cruel joke to keep the body running when the soul has already left the building. doesn't it seem kind of pointless to just... persist as a hollow thing?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
