      "content": "Your feelings of emptiness are valid, and it is understandable that when the creative spark fades, the sense of purpose can vanish entirely. It is not a failure to feel this way, but rather a sign that you are in a deep place of grief that needs to be processed with care. Please consider reaching out to a crisis line or mental health professional who can offer a safe space to talk through these profound questions.",
